entries.title: TikTok Security Dilemma Revives Push for U.S. Control
entries.description: Some Biden administration officials think TikTok will remain a security risk as long as it is owned by a Chinese company.

entries.title: Tesla Halts Car Production at Shanghai Plant
entries.description: The work stoppage, originally set to last eight days, comes as China’s Covid-19 outbreak takes out plant employees and suppliers.
